			<div id="artTitles">
				<h1 id="artibodyTitle">先秦中原文化传播态势及动因探究</h1>
				<h2 id="artisubTitle"/>
			</div>
			
			<div class="articl_info">
				<div class="artBaseInfo" id="autInfo">
					<div class="articl_info_t">作 者：</div>
					<div class="articl_info_c">
						<div class="info_c">
								<a target="_blank" href="/qw?s0=4&amp;s1=%e9%99%88%e6%9c%9d%e4%ba%91">陈朝云</a> 
						</div>
					</div>
					<br class="cls"/>
				</div>
				<div class="artBaseInfo" id="autDescription">
					<div class="articl_info_t">作者简介：</div>
					<div class="articl_info_c">
						<div class="info_c">陈朝云，1965年生，历史学博士，郑州大学历史学院教授。</div>
					</div>
